isDebugEnabled

boolean isDebugEnabled()
This method should be called to prevent from performing expensive operations (such as String concatenation) when the logger level is more than debug.

Returns:
true if the DEBUG level of the service is enabled.

isTraceEnabled

boolean isTraceEnabled()
This method should be called to prevent from performing expensive operations (such as String concatenation) when the logger level is more than trace.

Returns:
true if the TRACE level of the service is enabled.
